version_description: I didn't find any Tab with Full Chords for an soft acoustic Version (only Powerchords), so I wrote it down. Also the syllable/chordchange is more accurate. Watch: https://youtu.be/nwSzIIa5Tus.
This is the (best) version of the song that was played live on VH1 Storytellers.
Chords are not added to all verses in version 1. One verse is missing. Instrumental part is inaccurate. The other versions are incorrect in tune and have missing chords.
Drop D tuning. Capo for original key of recording. Makes it a lot easier to play this song.

song_name: All The Love In The World
